      p.lead Open Budget: Oakland visualizes the city's current and past budget data into accessible charts for the public. Data is published by the city. See Oakland's #[a(href='/budget-visuals.html') previous budgets], as well as the city's #[a(href='https://magic.piktochart.com/output/5111124-oakland-5-year-forecast-16-20-' target='_blank') five-year forecast].

      .well
